data.description: Welcome to 2903 N. Magellan Dr! This updated & move-in ready ranch features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, under cabinet lighting, ample counter space & a breakfast bar. An abundance of natural light from the large windows & open concept living create a sense of serenity throughout. Dining room just off the kitchen has plenty of room for entertaining. The woodburning stone fireplace in the living room creates a cozy space to snuggle up with loved ones on those cold winter nights. The primary suite offers a private bath with double vanity sinks, whirlpool tub & walk-in closet.  Partial basement is being used as an art studio right now, but could be a great workshop or office too! Fenced yard features a spacious deck, play set, & storage shed.  This is a nice & quiet community with a private association beach & boat slips in walking distance from the home. Per McHenry County, a garage is possible if you choose to build one! Come enjoy lake living & watch some amazingly beautiful sunsets at the beach without the high taxes of waterfront living! Whether you are searching for a year-round home or a possible investment property/summer house, this home checks all the boxes. This home is not in flood plain. No HS contingencies please.
